                      Docker
                      ======

This template will enable the kernel features for docker and build
containerd and docker into the file system.  The containerd and
dockerd systemd services will be started up automatically.

You can inspect the kernel configuration on a running device when
logged is a root by running:

  wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/moby/moby/master/contrib/check-config.sh
  chmod 755 check-config.sh
  ./check-config.sh


You can test docker's functionality by running:

  docker run hello-world


